      "webPublicationDate":"2013-08-30T17:32:15Z",
      "webTitle":"BlackBerry sales hit by fears over company's future",
      "webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/aug/30/blackberry-sales-concerns-company-future",
